data.description: In the heart of Noda, discover charm, convenience, and an income-generating potential. Just a few steps away, Amelie's beckons, along with a plethora of dining options in the vibrant NODA neighborhood. A brief stroll leads you to the Lynx Blue Line 36th St. Station & seamless connectivity to entertainment, dining, and the upcoming grocery store. The detached 2nd Living Quarter includes a 4th bedroom, flex space, bath, laundry, kitchen, attic, & storage—a perfect solution for working from home, accommodating guests, in-laws, au pairs, or expanding into an Airbnb, elevating the total HLA Sf to over 2570 SF. (486 Sq. Ft. not included in the HLA is, in fact completely HVAC/electrically equipped). The covered porch adds a delightful touch for entertainment, dining, and hosting, while two contemporary garage doors enhance versatility, creating an open and airy atmosphere. Rarely does one find an income-generating space as versatile and appealing as this!
